      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a refined balance of performance and long-term reliability. This unit demonstrates consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved cabin, reflecting a history of diligent ownership. It represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a sophisticated automotive solution. Fully inspected and prepared for immediate acquisition.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
