    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved and maintained over the years. It runs like a dream and is totally ready to hit the road for some new adventures with you! It's the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend trips. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L straight-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and optimized via the double VANOS variable valve timing system. The chassis remains composed thanks to reinforced subframe mounting points and a fresh set of bushings, ensuring the M Variable Differential Lock translates torque effectively to the tarmac. Recent service includes a valve clearance adjustment and rod bearing replacement, addressing critical preventative maintenance. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains tight, the throttle response is telepathic, and the suspension geometry is dialed for spirited apex-hunting. A true driver\u2019s spec for those who value mechanical pedigree over concours perfection.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. No accidents. Ready for pickup.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
